title: Phil Hendrie - Phil's First Show (1993-03-25) + Bonus Show 1994-
description:
PhilHendrieShow.com Audio Archive - Phil's First Show (1993-03-25) + Bonus Show 1994-03-12

The very first Phil Hendrie Show broadcast on WCCO in Minneapolis, Minnesota on March 25th, 1993.  Also includes a complete bonus show also from WCCO from March 12th, 1994.  Downloaded from the audio archive on PhilHendrieShow.com.  These shows are very rare, there's not much audio out there from this early in Phil's career.
